methods.convert:
Converts between the value in the column and the return value of the provider.

:param v: (java.lang.Object) - value in the column
:return: (java.lang.Double) value in the column converted to return type of the provider

text:
IndexableData dataset whose data is a column in a SwappableTable and whose indices are the row
 numbers of the column.

 Data values are converted to doubles.
